sentences.english: Force is a physical power, and I fail to see what moral effect it can have.
sentences.chinese: 強力是一種物質力量，我看不出它具有什麼道德後果。

sentences.english: The mends on your shirt were almost invisible.
sentences.chinese: 你襯衣上修補的地方簡直看不出來。

sentences.english: I do my best to never, ever look like a crook.
sentences.chinese: 我盡一切所能讓你根本看不出我是個騙子。
你就看不出來它已經是半死不活了嗎？

sentences.english: But with a hologram, you can't see how light plays on the surface of the car.
sentences.chinese: 但在全息圖上看不出光打在車身上的效果。

sentences.english: After six months, I couldn't see the value in it.
sentences.chinese: 六個月後，我看不出念這個書的價值何在。

sentences.english: As long as they are good fakes, other people won't know any different.
sentences.chinese: 只要假貨不露餡，別人也就看不出差別。

sentences.english: He, however, didn’t see any practical application for it in life.
sentences.chinese: 但是，他也看不出這個課在生活中有什麼實際的應用。

sentences.english: Drouet was not shrewd enough to see that this was not tactful.
sentences.chinese: 杜洛埃不夠精明，看不出這麼做太沒有策略了。

sentences.english: And then the children remembered that Martha couldn't see the wishes.
sentences.chinese: 於是孩子們記起馬莎是看不出這些許願的事的。

sentences.english: The sum is wrong, but I can’t see where I went wrong.
sentences.chinese: 總數錯了，可是我看不出哪裏算錯了。

sentences.english: The silk thread cans not see clearly is which house, but affirmation comes from Chiang-Nan.
sentences.chinese: 絲線看不出來是哪家的，但肯定是從江南來的。

sentences.english: However, with her new face I can't see her going any further.
sentences.chinese: 然而，我看不出帶着她的新臉孔她還能走多遠。

sentences.english: Is it octagonal copper pole?I can't see it from pics only.
sentences.chinese: 是八棱銅杆的？從圖片看不出那不對。

sentences.english: I cannot see any improvement in your writing.
sentences.chinese: 看不出你的寫作有什麼起色。
